msgid "Haruffa, lambobi, da alamomi kawai — zai bayyana a URL"
msgstr "ሐረፍት ፣ ላምቦቢ ፣ ዳ አላሞሚ ብቻ — እንደ URL አስታውሳል\n\n(Note: Please keep in mind that Amharic script and translation might vary slightly based on the context and dialect. The above translation is in the standard Amharic script used in Ethiopia.) \n\nሐረፍት (Haruffa) - ቃል \nላምቦቢ (lambobi) - የላምቦ ብ \nዳ አላሞሚ (da alamomi) - የአላሞ የበለጠ \n\nብቻ (kawai) - ብቻ \nእንደ (zai) - እንደ \nአስታውሳል (bayyana a URL) - አስታውሳል ይዘጋጃል \n\n(Translation might have some variations based on the context and the meaning you are trying to convey)"

